For many businesses that dont have the time or the resources to manage HR functions, outsourcing is a cost-effective alternative to hiring an in-house human resources staff. Todays HR firms offer a wide variety of services to companies that need to focus on their core business activities and still establish and maintain good HR policies. To decide if HR outsourcing is right for you, ask yourself three questions.
